item.title: Alexia Roditis (Destroy Boys)
item.description: Episode 363 – Alexia Roditis of Destroy Boys joins the show today! We get into their story, from childhood & early influences, starting the band, to now being a role model for many playing huge festivals & opening for legendary artists like blink-182. Catch them at Lollapalooza this saturday (their set will be streaming on Hulu), and the new album “Funeral Soundtrack #4” drops August 9th! Shampoo sucks! It dries out and strips your hair of essential oils... Feed: https://feeds.feedburner.com/LeadSingerSyndrome
